00:41:52.080 --> 00:41:54.950
But let me tell you which
source it will not be.

00:41:54.950 --> 00:41:56.720
It will not be the marketer.

00:41:56.720 --> 00:42:02.860
It won't be M as the source
for information about quality.

00:42:02.860 --> 00:42:05.180
And it's not that marketers
are perceived necessarily

00:42:05.180 --> 00:42:07.740
as crooks or dishonest.

00:42:07.740 --> 00:42:10.880
It's simply because the
marketer, by definition,

00:42:10.880 --> 00:42:12.010
has vested interests.

00:42:12.010 --> 00:42:17.430
So you look for alternative
sources of information.

00:42:17.430 --> 00:42:20.700
10, 15 years ago those
were very limited.

00:42:20.700 --> 00:42:22.475
What we experienced
in the past 10,

00:42:22.475 --> 00:42:25.850
15 years is an explosion
in the availability of O,

00:42:25.850 --> 00:42:27.700
and this is not going away.

00:42:27.700 --> 00:42:30.435
So you may see movement
within O. People

00:42:30.435 --> 00:42:33.810
will stop trusting one
source of information

00:42:33.810 --> 00:42:35.990
and will move to another.

00:42:35.990 --> 00:42:39.330
For example, if people
in general stop trusting

00:42:39.330 --> 00:42:44.100
