00:42:48.910 --> 00:42:51.400
Currently, there are no
signs that people are not

00:42:51.400 --> 00:42:52.320
trusting reviews.

00:42:52.320 --> 00:42:59.270
In fact, there is evidence
that people definitely

00:42:59.270 --> 00:43:00.120
trust reviews.

00:43:00.120 --> 00:43:03.040
And the reason, I
believe, is simple.

00:43:03.040 --> 00:43:08.070
Overall reviews do reflect
the general concept

00:43:08.070 --> 00:43:11.610
of a place, a general
idea about the product.

00:43:11.610 --> 00:43:13.920
Is it 100% accurate?

00:43:13.920 --> 00:43:16.810
Absolutely not,
but you get an idea

00:43:16.810 --> 00:43:19.240
of what your likely
experience is

00:43:19.240 --> 00:43:22.370
going to be when
you read reviews.

